      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<h3 id=\"VariationofInstancesinMaya-PxrVary\">PxrVary</h3><p>The <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661737\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrVary</a> pattern allows for random variation.  Let's try varying the color of the teacups based on the Particle ID.</p><p>Select the nParticleShape1 node. Look under the Instancer attributes. Change the Object Index from None to Particle ID.</p><p>This causes a primvar called particleId to be available on the instances.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"299\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesParticleID.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549822&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=299&amp;height=597\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544539792/rfmInstancesParticleID.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549822&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"869\" data-width=\"435\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539841\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmInstancesParticleID.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544539792\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"f0cdcddc-0bf3-42c7-8ed9-2c713f87d2bd\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesParticleID.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549822&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=435&amp;height=869 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesParticleID.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549822&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=299&amp;height=597 1x\"></span><p /><p>Next, wire a PxrVary pattern into the color of the material used for each of the cup and the saucer.</p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544539792/rfmInstancesPxrVary.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549821&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544539792/rfmInstancesPxrVary.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549821&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"86\" data-width=\"383\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539838\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmInstancesPxrVary.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544539792\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"9ab947b8-b63b-467f-98fb-8adf86f9a6aa\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><p /><p>Set up the PxrVary to use the particleId as its seed for randomization.  </p><ul><li><p>Change the Vary Source to Primvar.</p></li><li><p>Type in <strong>particleId</strong> as the Variable Name.</p></li><li><p>Move the Hue slider value to 1, for maximum variation of the hue.<br/><br/></p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"367\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesPxrVaryAE.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550003&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=367&amp;height=245\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544539792/rfmInstancesPxrVaryAE.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550003&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"297\" data-width=\"444\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539844\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmInstancesPxrVaryAE.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544539792\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"54a0a98e-b306-43d5-ba43-0876b4acc2e9\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesPxrVaryAE.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550003&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=444&amp;height=297 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesPxrVaryAE.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550003&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=367&amp;height=245 1x\"></span><p>Now the render looks like this:</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"394\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesPxrVaryRender.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550003&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=394&amp;height=295\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544539792/rfmInstancesPxrVaryRender.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550003&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"480\" data-width=\"640\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539847\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmInstancesPxrVaryRender.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544539792\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"e74a1336-1c10-4aaa-87cd-bf50f65cf400\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesPxrVaryRender.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550003&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=640&amp;height=480 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesPxrVaryRender.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550003&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=394&amp;height=295 1x\"></span>"
